{"tid":1307804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急] 有冇人識高登嘅啊笛","createTime":"2019-07-11T17:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T17:52:10.000Z","uid":27319,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"19190367938133dd218d045fcaa603a55e6015dc","tid":1307804,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"大家唔好介意佢係高登仔，佢正話搞完BNO平權啲嘢，就喺個谷話要了結自己。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7082603&amp;type=BW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7082603%26type%3DBW&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=c81e5d7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7082603&amp;type=BW</a><br />\n<br />\n求大家幫忙搵搵佢宜家喺邊，因為我地唔想失去多一個戰友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求大家幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7081653&amp;type=BW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7081653%26type%3DBW&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=f6b1ff34\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7081653&amp;type=BW</a>"},{"pid":"e7b19fbec6ff9f0348e6099be6abd5730531e63e","tid":1307804,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:07:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"544c87a23c25a1b67891af0fff50e70a8fa2147b","tid":1307804,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:07:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c8ac3ecb406509e2af71306466026e54ef21215","tid":1307804,"uid":8075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23845f3fff87a4f57be20d6de470eb87d7cec5c1","tid":1307804,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:11:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"692f5d5c40deed4b0a23b10247683b661bae298d","tid":1307804,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36d49ad3d1963cfa50c6e84961a8a70faf84de1","tid":1307804,"uid":275887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c32a77de4c326bac5e15adcd9c9dc6601c65118","tid":1307804,"uid":138296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d2259d3b473e475fb8782e01b9a6646bebd058ee","tid":1307804,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"692f5d5c40deed4b0a23b10247683b661bae298d","tid":1307804,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:17:39.000Z","msg":"聽識佢嘅谷友講佢有長期病患同depression，呢排又食唔到嘢，跟著做埋平權啲嘢之後喺個谷話要放開一切，tag佢又唔應。<br />\n<br />\n但係谷友話畀佢靜一靜就應該冇事，希望真係冇事，我地真係一個也不能少。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f14dc1d2ff127882ceb41682a647bef25f7ec5","tid":1307804,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpM2Q8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpM2Q8.png&h=f5bc83df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初見到佢留言見佢情況真係好差，係後尾有識佢嘅人喺個gp話畀佢靜下應該冇事，我又怕打擾到佢，所以唯有暫時等佢上水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望佢吉人自有天相。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}